    "12661787350178732006/12/24 00:19:06darksmirfOn my level 28 pally I soloed this. Once I aggroed him and the 2 mobs I just strafed (to keep from getting dazed) while hitting him with judgments and auto-attacks. Once my health got low I bubbled and by then I was at the tower with the guards to assist me so all I had to do was heal myself and let them kill him. Worked well.",
