  ["... and Bugs40"] = {
    "125814033npcMorgan Stern4794npcMorgan Stern47943150Stormwind250112602120431258",
    "1258166191411451372007/10/11 23:03:18FaaRThis quest purposefully sends you across the world so you can do the other quests available in Swamp of Sorrows; there's a fair amount of them at the Harborage along the northern mountain range for example. It's not such a pain if you take the opportunity to do these other quests first before returning back to Theramore. The swamp is also a heaven for Herbalists; well worth a visit just for this fact. There's also some iron and mithril to be found here; particulary in the Murloc cave to the southeast between Stonard and the ocean shore.\
\
Watcher Biggs (http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=5476) sits a little south of the road that leads forks off down to the Blasted Lands and to Stonard. He offers a short quest chain, one part of which also takes you to the beach, so to save time you do the first two parts of his chain before going for the crab legs.\
\
Galen Goodward (http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=5391) sits in a cage at the easternmost edge of the Broken encampment (Fallow Sanctuary). He wants to be escorted out of there, but unfortunately he also wants to be escorted through pretty much the densest part of the encampment. Bring friends or he'll die (though he can be buffed/healed). Do this quest when Biggs sends you here to look for his lost junk.\
\
Be sure to stumble upon Noboru the Cudgel. (http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=5477) He patrols around the middle-ish section of the swamp with two escorts and drops an item that starts another quest.\
\
There are also crates scattered around the swamp that can be looted for another quest-starting item. Take this item, run/ride back to Darkshire just after you finish Biggs' quest chain and find the NPC near the town center standing next to the eastern road that wants you to take a crate to the castle in Blasted Lands to turn in another three quests.\
\
More quests to do in Swamp of Sorrows:\
Mazen's Behest, found in Stormwind's Mage Quarter at the canals, in a house right next to the entrance to Stockades: http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=1363\
\
In Search of the Temple, also in Stormwind from a dwarf in the bar in the Dwarf quarter. You find him through the door immediately to your right when entering the Dorf quarter when coming from the direction of the Keep. His friend standing nearby hands out quests to the Deadmines by the way.\
\
Dream Dust in the Swamp, from Krazek in Booty Bay (he stands in the inn): http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=1116\
\
Ledger from Tanaris, starts at the wooden outhouse in Searing Gorge. (http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=4450) Be sure to be level 43 and bring 15 Silk Cloth before going there.\
\
Doing all these quests gives you a grand total of five quests to hand in at Nethergarde Keep and a bucketload of experience.",
