    "11146192714101927142007/11/28 10:37:28JineiJust a handy trick for warlocks doing this quest: replace CoA with some other curse (preferably Curse of Weakness) just before 20%, this prevents those last big ticks from killing the raptor.",
    "11146207623102076232007/12/26 13:11:46SnikmordRaptors are found just north across the river from Sergeant Lukas. Use the Sturdy Rope on the raptors when chat window says they're ready for capture or when they call for help (this happens when their health hits 10-20% approx.). It would be advisable to go easy on the DoT (damage-over-time) spells if you are a caster as it is VERY easy to accidentally kill the raptors instead of capturing them. It is allegedly possible to capture more than one raptor at once sometimes if there are others nearby, but this might be a bug. I don't know whether or not this has been fixed.",
