    "9518204105202041052007/12/19 19:06:27tHeBlAcKpArAdEok, so the scouts and deforesters are easy to find, the Warsong Shredders weren't, i found one at the labor camp. didn't find another one so i waited for that one to spawn back and killed it again. but Overseer Gorthak will be easy to find. just pass this big building there. if you can stealth, stealth through. if not. happy fighting. any who, go to the building NEXT to the big building up the stairs and whack away at the evil orc who is located at 88,59. have fun! :)",
    "951820484221418912007/12/21 04:51:21brasshopperFirst time in I went to the big building next to the one that he was in.  Inside the building, the drops were very good from mobs that were one or two levels higher than similar mobs outside but they could be soloed (except possibly from the pit where I decided not to try single pulling). Second time I paid more attention to the exact coordinates. The Overseer is in sort of a little tower and I had to enter the tower to get line of sight. He was L30, but not nearly as tough as other L30s in the area. He runs, like the rest of them.\
\
