    "292641324041322006/11/24 17:06:59contentiousIn order to do this quest you need to have the flask ready, with either your bag open or on one of your action bars. When one of the caster Troggs begins to cast his spell(his hands will glow green) right click the flask. You'll collect the goo. He'll still shoot you though, so be ready to take him down after that.",
