    "3964919220491922007/03/10 15:08:39zwirdgiI did this quest at level 20, got runs through VC, Stocks, and got a high level to help me kill the 2 30 ish guys at the end. Even though i spent about 5hrs and 5 or 6 deaths on this quest tree, it was majorly worth it when i got my hands on this ring :).",
