    "396146343101463432007/08/30 00:57:16ilyaieQuest ends at 78,17 :D ( Lady Katrana Prestor )",
    "3967805920780592007/05/05 06:16:34LieandraI ran through this line (still need the duskwood and redridge parts), but want to put a little clarity here.\
\
The quest tells you to speak to \"King Varian Wrynn\". A search here for that King does not find you anything. \
