    "3961820410182042006/12/27 23:01:37swotamThis quest rewards 500 Stormwind reputation as of patch 2.01",
    "396211333102113332008/01/02 02:36:53suicidechildeI got 3800xp and 550 rep for this mission.",
    "396174844301748442007/10/25 17:31:38HunnitFor twinks who have just learned of this, if your 19 you can still do the quest line and not pass 20, You just need a high level to take you through all the parts. (which will make it go faster AND eat up a lot of the Mob exp you'll get.). \
\
Started this questline again after I learned of the ring a few days ago, and at 19 I had to go back through DM to get the letter, but due to having a high level I just waited at the entrance for him to clear the instance, except for VC, then ran up and looted VC after he killed him, overall (because of the respawning pats) I got about 900 - 1000 exp, so thats not too bad. \
\
And you do the same thing for Stocks, which is easier because you dont have to worry about respawns as much. So unless your already close to leveling to 20, then I suggest you start the questline and get this ring.",
