this quest gives from 300 XP to 3000 XP",
    "694194143201941432007/11/30 20:15:11SecondChanceI'd just like to point out that the fastest way to this area is not actually entering Stromgarde Keep via the gate, or the crack in the wall on the right side. For those with Co-ords simply go to 21,72 (those without co-ords, while facing the entrance of the keep, turn left and run around the castle wall. You should reach a small alcove with the water in front of you. ) Upon reaching this point, while facing the water, if you turn right there is a somewhat steep hill that you can easily climb ( may be fiddly ) leading to a large gap in the wall. (gap co-ords 21,70) At this point you do not need to jump down. And will not agro ogres from the ground. Simply circle your way around to the location required and jump down at a valid entry point. This is only to amend the fact that this IS climbable and you do not need to make your way around along the hillside.",
    "694210644102106442007/12/31 19:24:05Minotauro28The drop rate may be low but i got it on the first mob that i killed....but the real problem aint getting in there but coming out of there because you cant get out from where you came in :S",
