    "96893331240333122007/02/09 19:53:40kanoQuite an easy fight; Solo'd him as a 19 rogue using only a Lesser Healing Potion. Only thing that remotely hurts is his flame breath which hit for 100. He also has a fear, so I'd recommend clearing the entire top of the hill.",
    "9689130547101305472007/08/01 15:01:48AnnitorchI just solo'd this on a 20 Draenei Frost Mage, first attempt. He's *not* immune to Frost Nova, so I just used that whenever I could to put some distance between us, though he does move very fast. I pelted him with as many Frostbolts as I could, using Fire Blast as well. I only used Mana Shield once and GotN, didn't use Cold Snap or Evocation, and I'm not specced for Frostbite, but I do have Imp. Frost Nova and Permafrost. With all this in mind, you should be able to take him down pretty fast if you use all your abilities well.",
    "96893560810356082007/02/14 01:18:02AshalSoloed 19 shaman, just make sure you have a healing potion of two.",
    "96892194310219432007/01/20 06:18:20Senei19 Priest and 18 Paladin totally owned him; this guy's a total pushover. I didn't even cast more then a single heal.",
    "9689114515401145152007/07/02 15:39:35mpoy70Follow the path (starts at 71 25) to the top of the hill where you will summon him. Easy fight (for lvl20 shaman).",
