    "5283140npcGrumnus Steelshaper5164npcGrumnus Steelshaper5164320",
    "5283114371101143712007/07/02 10:37:38BeslanIn response to learning Armorsmith. \
You dont need to select Armorsmith to learn Ornate Mithril plans.\
The Armorsmith quest is just a quest to create some armor Items to \"Prove your skill.\" He asks you right in it... \"You do know how to create Ornate Mithril, dont you?\"\
\
The other quests - One you get from Hank the Hammer or Ox are for \"The Mithril Order\" which is where you learn the Ornate Mithril stuff. Not to mention you get a pretty sweet smithing hammer!\
\
If you do the other quests (The Mithril order - Hank in SW or Ox in Org) you can learn Ornate Mithril and not even need to do the Armorsmithing quest. Also I think they are lower than the Armorsmith quest (Level and skill req) that you could do it before and not need to do it in one straight shot.",
    "5283176654201766542007/10/30 01:35:22hoffmaniNow you can respec from weaponsmith to armorsmith. It cost nothing but only gold. (110G total)\
