 Horde should go to [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=11178] Borgosh Corebender <Weaponsmith> [/url]at Orgrimmar. This step costs 10G.\
3)Alliance: Then speak with[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=11145]Myolor Sunderfury[/url]  (he stands right in the middle of the forge) he will let you choose to become weaponsmith again or turn to armorsmith. This is free and you will keep your skill level after respec.\
(sry I dont know where is the conterpart horde NPC, but should be around the BS trainer)",
    "52837671410767142007/05/02 16:58:38WarondarI held off on deciding to go either Armorsmith or Weaponsmith but completed a multitude of blacksmithing quests leading to these.\
