    "6589133620913362007/05/26 21:30:57SxerosThis is very easy quest. Immediatly when you accept it, just run straight to the south, and the courier will be walking there, surrounded by four of his guards. Well, my character is mage, so it's easy to just pick one. But most important thing on mage is: Use Ice Armor, not Mage Armor! \
