    "17981392021601392022007/08/16 21:59:59FairamayI dinged 30 this evening, and made the mistake to think I'd have the Felhunter in a flash. (It's almost 5 in the morning.) This is absolutely one of the most annoying quests I've ever done. Luckily I had the flight paths that were needed.\
\
The quest itself. (Alliance)\
\
First you get the quest at your warlock trainer. (Doh.)\
\
- He'll tell you to go talk to Strahad Farsan in Ratchet. (The Barrens.)\
< http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=6251 >\
\
- After doing that this guy tells you to go talk to Krom Stoutarm in Ironforge.\
< http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=6294 >\
\
- Krom'll ask you for 2 items, a Moldy Tome, found in Hillsbrad Foothills,\
< http://www.wowhead.com/?object=92013 >\
And a Tattered Manuscript, found in Thousand Needles.\
< http://www.wowhead.com/?object=92423 >\
\
( I put my Hearthstone in IF during this part, it saved me some walking. )\
\
- After you've received these two items you return to him. (Yes, Krom.)\
\
Out of these two items he'll craft the tome, and tells you to go fetch 3 Rod of Channeling,\
< http://www.wowhead.com/?item=6930 >\
Dropped by Dragonmaw Bonewarders and Dragonmaw Shadowwarders in Wetlands.\
< http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=1057 >\
\
You have to bring these items back to Strahad Farsan in Ratchet, where you'll summon a Felhunter, and kill it. After you've done áll that you get to summon your very own. Hooray.",
