    "47445760190457602007/03/03 22:21:02TenyaHe's standing at a ring of tents which have level 28 and 29 non-elites. You can sneak up the hill behind him from the road (near a tree guarded by a level 21 slime) and avoid having to clear to him through the camp. There are a couple mobs near him you can pull solo. Depending on your pull timing and clearing you can get Nek'rosh with two, one, or none of the other mobs at the camp.\
