    "2611749370174932006/12/20 03:29:39SybaekThis area is full of level 37-38 skellys that you have to kill.  They have fear protection.  But they are easy to kill, they don't wander very far and their respawn timer is on the slow side.  The level 39 necromancers that walk around might give you some trouble, they patrol the little valley.  Contrary to the comment above, you DO NOT lose reputation with Magram.  I've killed over 30 of these, including the necromancers, and have lost no reputation.",
