    "228202039102020392007/12/15 21:15:23greatscottI soloed Mor'Ladim as a 32 fire mage. I waited for him in the clearing east of his path and hit him as he was walking away with pyroblast, fireball, and cone of cold and he was on me. Then frost nova, backed up and cast mana shield and fireballed him again, then fireblast, he broke out of the frost nova, then arcane explosion, got off another fireball while he was pounding on me, then fireblast, frost nova again, backed up, bandaged, used a mana agate, another fireball and fireblast and down he went.",
    "228211572102115722008/01/02 12:15:42shockabishi could find a group so i soloed him as a 30 elemental shaman. sat down stoneskin, searing and poison cleaning totem. i thought he would be poisoning too since the other guys did but he didnt. i had a protection agilty and stamina scroll so i used those as well. i healed myself when i was half way down in my hp twice and use gift of naruu. i kept frost shocking him to slow him down. went down real nice and on the first time. good luck :)",
