    "9764891630489162007/03/09 23:32:25CrystalisThis thing really should show a group needed in the quest log.  He *says* \"if you and others act as my guards\" and he means it.  First time I tried I got to the second mob spawn, which is 3 undead scouts.  I didn't realize one of them was on the NPC instead of me and he died right as I killed the second mob.  Second time I tried, I had them all on me (level 24 druid) and killed them.  I'm on a PvP server and there had been a ?? shaman running around that had killed me earlier so we set off towards the border, I'm scanning over my shoulder hoping we'll hit friendly territory.  We do, and I start to breathe easier.  Sadly, about 5 seconds later 3 named satyr pop out, one summons an imp, they all start casting spells (2 at the NPC, the third on me as I charged him in bear) and before I had the guy at half life, the NPC was dead.  I died shortly thereafter, and about the only good news there is that I was 10 feet from the closest graveyard.  Don't do this quest without at least 2 people, maybe even 3 for the fight at the end.",
