    "610146244201462442007/08/29 20:39:14TartaranI am a level 34 hunter. After attempting all of the prescribed methods and failing miserably, I went through Booty Bay. I jumped off the dock of the boat to Ratchet, swam around the headland to the north to where his camp is, and climbed on to the rock jutting out of the water. Pull \"Pretty Boy\" to you with an arrow swim into the water so he gets further from the gang had my pet attack and just lesurely shot his carcass back into hell.",
    "6106937410693742007/04/18 22:55:46pwn3dI got lucky soloing this as a level 37 druid.  Stealthing past the mobs and swimming out to a position off the beach opposite Duncan, I made sure that he was just inside spell range.  Once the surrounding mobs were at their furthest distance from Duncan, I cast a Moonfire on him.  This pulled him out into the water without aggroing any of the mobs.",
