    "16611264180112642006/12/08 14:40:13bangyHorde can do Deadmines too... Shamans are possible\
\
Vancleef isn't too hard if done well. You'll have encountered harder bosses and areas in the instance, such as the large tauren captain who stuns, and the upper deck with Cookie and his friends. Apart from the rogues, he isn't too hard to kill. Just be prepared.\
