    "1080116335101163352007/07/06 05:18:00mpoy70The wagon to blow with the red explosives is at 75 57. The letters are on a crate at 74 59 near the mine entrance. Keep in mind that not all mobs guarding the letters will run away from them because of the explosion, so there will be 2-3 more to clear before you can loot them. Also there is one mob patroling the area in and out of the mine entrance. If you die the first time (like me) you can forget about explosives and clear the mobs the old fashioned way :)",
