do your thing on morbent, heis quite easy without his aura, use evasion if necessary, I only lost 30% of my hp.",
    "55212004102120042008/01/03 04:07:21Meigas007This guy was a piece of cake after you deactivate his shield.  Lol, at first I forgot to do that and my group and I were getting rocked.  By the time I remembered to use it and the cool down was done, one of my group was dead and the other was running and we had barely scratched him.  The weapon took him down to about 70% life and I rocked him in a few seconds as a lvl 30 mage with a few fireballs and fire blast.  You can definitely solo this!",
    "555474720547472007/03/21 09:50:33BredesenYou can solo this at level 34 maybe lower. Coords: 17, 33\
\
You just take out 2 of the guards in the room, then die. Go res, kill 2 more, then die. Go res and now you have Morbent all alone, and if you have some shadow resistance, you can kill him without problems.",
    "55187026401870262007/11/18 12:46:12BoronaThey removed his adds with Patch 2.3.0 if i'm not mistaken.\
