    "55194322311927802007/12/01 07:42:47GratisI took im down as a lvl 30 Mage, he was much easier then I expected. He will counter spell one of your spells so I just started to cast fireball to get him to waste his counter spell, then I hit him with a long string of arcane missiles.",
    "55114932301149322007/07/03 11:13:18psycoticSoloed as a 29 feral druid in bear form.  The trick was to focus on the adds first, and use line of sight for morbent's casting (i used either side of the doorway to block sight).  I died once on the first pull with all 3 adds, but had finished off 1 of the mobs before I died.  Came back with just 2 adds and morbent, used line of sight again until the adds were dead, then finished him off.  Used 1 health pot, but probably didn't need it.",
