    "18021787922111932007/11/04 00:30:59RedwoodElfThe Mouldy Tome is called \"Tome of Cabal\" when you mouseover it, and can be found in the one of the three closest Murloc villages to Purgation Isle, south of Azureload Mine (Random placement.)\
