 I much prefer to give landmark directions rather than coordinates. Coordinates have their limitations, and don't work for everyone (and also, the coordinates in this game give no indication of altitude, which is critical for locations inside caves...you could search for hours at the \"above ground\" location if you only have the coordinates, when they're actually underground (If you need proof, go to the southern side of the Swamp of Sorrows with a miner, and try to find the minerals you see near Stonard.) Landmarks work for everyone.",
