    "303190807201908072007/11/25 04:58:05bronThese can also be found in another encampment - Direforge Hill. The mobs are much more manageable. Coords are 63.30 (southeast of Dun Modr, along the hills).  I did not run across any elite mobs in this area. I'm not sure if this encampment is new as of 2.3.",
