    "9851164051162006/11/29 07:01:38XFGREAPERStalvan Mismantle, to find him, take the road out of town to redridge. Take the first left and he is located in the house.  Once you have killed all of the others around him and he attacks be ready because he has a very quick attack time and if your a caster using DOT's use instant or you will never get them off. Exhaustion or a Frost buff of some sort will help.",
