    "98177693101776932007/11/01 11:42:45lv2fishYou will get 13,250 Quest turn in XP for the entire quest line from start to finish.",
    "98199655101996552007/12/11 13:17:15wowisashYou can find Stalvan Mistmantle at [b][77,35][/b] his a lvl 32 and has 3 other people around him kill them first before going after him,but watch out for Stalvan running away at the end.  He'll run towards the Fetid Corpses and then you have more to fight at once. Also there is a chest hidden by the Manor at [b][79,33][/b].  Not a lot in it, but it's a decent bonus.",
