    "98125334101253342007/07/23 05:16:24SomewhereDid this as a level 29 assassination spec'd Rogue after just hitting 29.\
\
Way I did it:\
\
a) Clear area around him\
\
b) Wait for him to go into house\
\
c) Stealth and get as close as you can, he can detect you but it will be close enough to keep him in the house.\
\
d) Pop Evasion and start waking away with Sinister Strike.\
\
e) 5x Combo points = Expose Armor from then on use combo points for Eviscerate.\
\
d) Pop a Greater Healing Potion as required.\
\
From there on he runs at about 15% health, he just ran into the wall inside the house and I took him down easily after that, but he is tough as hell.\
\
Very nice XP.",
