    "9504113147101131472007/06/30 00:43:03DarythIt easy, i just had to kill one mob and he was level 22. There are two mobs that circle the area, one in the water one around the fountain, if you keep an eye out for those two you should be fin. Level 20 shammy by the way.",
    "95047034011643572007/04/21 02:31:50SugarwoodA few things to remember when taking on this quest.  If you're dying, it's because you're letting them get the big hits in.  Stop their casts with your Earth Shock, and only use it when they're casting.\
\
