\
Just keep a Stoneskin totem down, and you should be fine.  I went down about 310 hp every fight, so be sure to use some of your quicker heals.",
    "95046190920619092007/04/04 08:13:17JavenEasy to solo as a 20 shaman.  Just interrupt their lightning bolts/entangling roots with earth shock (right before they finish casting so you spend the least time being beat on) and watch for adds.\
\
I'd also recommend setting your hearth to Blood Watch so you don't have to run all the way back to Aqueous.",
