    "950413092531210462007/08/02 07:36:45GambrinStacks well with the http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=1034  - the Ruins of Stardust quest (#3 in the chain) from Pelturas Whitemoon, Astranaar, Ashenvale, Azeroth ;-)  Chain starts at Mystra's Point on your way to Astranaar, with http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=1010 - Bathran's Hair (BTW the chain is not linked here on wowhead.com) . For L20-23 shammy this chain is a very good way of spending your time on your way to the Water Totem.",
