    "11209187726301877262007/11/19 14:44:52dlanodGo to the shipwreck he describes and apply the fish paste. Swim around the shipwreck until a level 37 Lurking Shark appears and attacks you. The shark appeared for me at 55, 63, over the southern end of the wreck. Be careful when swimming away because I swam over the place again, and the shark respawned on me. Kill the shark and quest done.\
