    "219169044101690442007/10/15 11:31:54adashielI believe it's quests like these that led Blizzard to turn BC escorts into Group quests by default.  As others mentioned above me, the Corporal will happily attempt to take on far more mobs than he can handle.  It's a taste of what you'll later go through [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10284]escorting Thrall from Old Durnholde[/url].  On the plus side, this escort has no spawned ambushes, so you'll just be dealing with mobs that are already there.  Thus, on a crowded day, when the mobs are being mowed down as fast as they can spawn, this quest is effortless.  On the other hand, if you're the only one there it's a real grinder.",
