    "970151988101519882007/09/12 07:48:27CailenIt only took me about 10 kills to get the orb, however I was doing it on a level 22 priest and the mobs with the void walkers were impossible for me to take down. I ignored them and only killed the mobs with the imps and the excavators. I recommend that if you're having problems with the quest you do the same. It may take a tad longer, but totally worth it in the end (because you won't be dying constantly).",
