    "970196278101962782007/12/05 05:50:59brasshopperI soloed this with an untwinked 19 priest. It was all I could do to take down a lock-pet pair (I could get the lock-void walker pairs, but they were tough, low health and mana at the end of the fight. 15 DPS wand. Start with a shield, DD spell, dot, dot, and wand. When the shield comes down, stop, shield, renew, dot, wand, ignoring the pet. When the master died, shield, dot, heal, wand.  I finally managed to clean the warlock free area at 31,31 and then got the next several pops - and then one popped while I was killing another and I died - could not keep a shield up. \
