    "101725439110254392007/01/27 00:57:27childermassIf you start in Astranaar, head east on the main road. Toward WSG. Head down that road toward the entrance to the barrens. As you pass down the road you will come to a gate with Horde guards. At this point just swing over to the left of the gate with the Horde Guards, and you'll see the hole that you can waltz right in. \
\
