\
Keep making your way to the top and you'll come across a bunch of lvl 11-13 horde acolytes. Try and pull them one by one and they'll go down quick. Make your way to the top and you'll find the guy in possession of the head you need. Trap him if you can. If not, you're gonna be chasing him all around. His little minions can get you if you don't take him down fast.",
