    "540173411017342006/10/10 19:05:33DoranosYou can actually solo this quest without even dieing.  I did this at level 34 with no problem and no deaths.  To do this go in the building with the book case.  When the level 40 elite ogre aggros on you run outside of the building and take a right and go around the side of the building and then run westward along the side of the hill away from the building.  Do not attack the ogre so it loses aggro.  Once it does, the ogre will not have a clear path back to it's starting location.  It will then freeze and become temporarily evasion bugged. As soon as you see it stop, run back to the building and you should have just enough time to grab the book before the ogre is ported back inside the building.",
