    "102520239911728012007/12/16 14:44:02psycherhexicIt's not just when you hit them AND these debuffs knock you out of stealth. Trying to get an opener off on these guys is nearly an exercise in futility. So ridiculous. If you manage to sap one you can stand by them and the debuff will keep refreshing over and over while they are sapped. In Dark Age of Camelot we called these types of spells pulsing PBAoEs I believe. This is the only one I have seen in WoW, though I would bet there are a few more.\
