    "1710146104201461042007/08/29 15:08:47Soldier45The eggs required for this quest are lying around on the ground in Highperch of Thousand Needles. They look like hatched eggs.",
    "1710185389101853892007/11/15 20:50:00metalbunnyThe ramp to get to the plateau starts at 14,33. There's a big Tauren totem pole where it is.\
\
As a lvl 30 fury/arms spec with several blues, the wyverns (lvl 28-29) prooved to put up a decent fight. And doing this quest without killing them is impossible, as they aggro far enough away that charging them is really difficult. On top of that, the shells you need are far apart and there's not that many of them, so you get to run around the place a couple times, killing a whole bunch of the wyverns.\
\
As of patch 2.3, the shells shimmer, making them a lot easier to find, and thanks to the lowered amount of XP needed to level, you may just gain a level or two killing your way through all the wyverns.\
\
Overall, soloable at lvl 30, but bring plenty of food and/or bandages. And be very careful taking on more than one wyvern at the time, they hit a lot harder than you'd think, and they poison you which slows down your attacks.",
