    "97369313069312006/12/06 02:48:31Shadow1pscThis guy is level 24 with (1) level 24 minion and (1) level 17 minion with plenty of other level 24 demons about too.\
\
You'll find him around 24,60 - just behind the mountains south of the Shrine of Aessina. There will be a pass that will take you into the mountain where he is.",
    "9732724310272432007/01/29 15:53:12RegginI solo'd this as a 23 human pally, it was pretty hard. Didn't die but healed a few times and used protection.",
